The government offers financial support with [the MCZ subsidy](https://www.rvo.nl/subsidies-financing/mcz). With this scheme you receive a 50% discount on cybersecurity investments, up to a maximum of €1,250. This allows you to take a maximum of €2,500 in security measures. An ideal step to strengthen your digital security. This subsidy is specifically intended for new investments, such as:
securing your network and WiFi;
setting up two-factor authentication;
implementing backup systems;
offering cyber awareness training for your team.

